# ExpressJs With TypeScript Setup 
    - step 1 : init Projct
        ```
        npm init

        ```
    - step 2 : Install dependencies
        ```
        npm install express --save
        npm install typescript --save-dev
        npm i -D @types/node @types/express

        ```
    - step 3: Generate tsconfig.json
        ```
        npx tsc --init

        ```
    - step 4 : Project structure 


